creator: Prendergast, James Emile Pierre, 1858-1945. (author)
description: Prendergast, James Emile Pierre: 1858-1945. Arrived in Manitoba, 1882; in Legislature almost continuously from 1885 to 1897; appointed a judge, 1897; served on Supreme Court of Saskatchewan, 1905-1910; returned to Manitoba, 1910; chief justice of Manitoba, 1930-1944 (Morgan, Canadian men and women of the time, 1912; Wallace, Dictionary of Canadian biography).
